    dc:description "FIG. 1. Besleria iara. A. Habit. B. Open Corolla showing stamens and staminode. C. Gynoecium and Nectary. D. Close up of the inflorescence and stem. E. Calyx and Corolla in side view. (A – E from G. E. Ferreira 355)." ;
